tenderTitle: AI Interviewing and Psychometric Assessment Platform for NHS England Workforce Development
description: NHS England seeks a vendor to provide an AI interviewing and psychometric assessment platform to support large-scale recruitment services across its workforce development programme. The platform must include automated video interviewing with AI scoring, psychometric testing modules, and leadership assessment tools for senior roles. Integration with existing HR systems and compliance with UK GDPR is mandatory. assessment center , 51419
